reviewText:
This product wouldn't work on my DVD player because it was a different region.
The seller should have said it was not from Region one (the United States).  I
wouldn't have bought and wasted my money.

this is a awesome movie. this movie picks up where the last one left off. the animation is awesome the story is great and the voice acting is good. this is yet another fun batman animated movie to watch. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do
